1
00:00:37,480 --> 00:00:40,480
It seems your luck isn't so good this time.

2
00:00:42,040 --> 00:00:44,160
The safe upstairs isn't mine.

3
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,440
Where did my video go?

4
00:00:49,160 --> 00:00:52,120
How did you guys manage to do that?

5
00:00:52,120 --> 00:00:53,320
We just did.

6
00:00:54,400 --> 00:00:55,280
But

7
00:00:56,080 --> 00:00:58,560
it did take some effort.

8
00:00:59,320 --> 00:01:01,200
I intentionally revealed

9
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,080
the location of the three of them to you.

10
00:01:02,080 --> 00:01:04,280
And then I pretended to be caught by you.

11
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:06,960
The purpose was to distract you

12
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:09,560
to buy An Ning some time.

13
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:12,920
Wait a minute.

14
00:01:15,160 --> 00:01:16,520
What is your plan?

15
00:01:17,360 --> 00:01:18,480
Step one.

16
00:01:19,080 --> 00:01:20,560
You can notify Ding Tian now.

17
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,200
Tell him

18
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:23,140
you found Wenjing's address.

19
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:24,120
Hello.

20
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:25,600
Understood.

21
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:43,610
Attorney An.

22
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:44,800
This is

23
00:01:45,240 --> 00:01:46,840
what Mr. Ding ordered.

24
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:48,240
He asked me to deliver it.

25
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:57,759
Open the door.

26
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:09,199
If your safe is forced open

27
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:10,880
or the password is entered incorrectly three times,

28
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:13,120
it triggers the self-destruct program

29
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:15,480
to destroy everything inside.

30
00:02:15,480 --> 00:02:16,120
So,

31
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:19,170
we don't dare to risk making a mistake.

32
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:22,040
We have to rely on you to tell us.

33
00:02:57,720 --> 00:02:59,200
You know the rest.

34
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:01,360
Anning called to threaten you.

35
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,360
You were fooled.

36
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,120
Hello, Lawyer An.

37
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:05,480
Give me back the video about me.

38
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:07,720
Go upstairs and open the safe.

39
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:09,040
We installed a small program

40
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:10,440
in your safe.

41
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:12,040
As soon as you enter the password,

42
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:15,400
it will be synced to An Ning's phone.

43
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:22,079
Qian Ya.

44
00:03:22,079 --> 00:03:22,560
Qian Ya.

45
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:37,280
I have one last question.

46
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:42,040
After doing all this,

47
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:47,000
what exactly are you after?

48
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:54,640
Peace of mind.

49
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,320
In life,

50
00:03:58,000 --> 00:04:00,000
isn't peace of mind what we all seek?

51
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,040
Alright.

52
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,440
My task is complete.

53
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:16,600
Let's leave the rest to the police.

54
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,760
Who are you?

55
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:19,920
I need your help with something.

56
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:21,480
What is it?

57
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,160
It's a long story.

58
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,480
Can we go inside to talk?

59
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,800
We need to figure out a way

60
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:34,400
to make him believe Meimei is really in danger.

61
00:05:34,520 --> 00:05:35,480
Then

62
00:05:36,159 --> 00:05:37,420
just cut off my finger.

63
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,440
That works.

64
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:40,200
Let's shoot a video.

65
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:41,960
I'll try to do some special effects

66
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:42,890
so it looks real.

67
00:05:47,159 --> 00:05:48,159
Found the finger.

68
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:51,800
I found it.

69
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:05,920
I learned how to make fried rice recently.

70
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:07,980
It tastes pretty good.

71
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:10,000
Also,

72
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:12,760
I ranked 17th in the class on the midterm.

73
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:15,040
Give me a little more time.

74
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:18,280
I'll try to make it to the top 10 by the finals.

75
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:27,200
Meimei,

76
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,080
I'm sorry.

77
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:33,700
What I promised you might have to be delayed for a few years.

78
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:38,280
When mom left,

79
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:40,700
you said she just went to work abroad.

80
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,560
It's the same now.

81
00:06:43,200 --> 00:06:45,530
I'll just pretend you went to work abroad.

82
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,200
Unlike mom,

83
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:50,260
you're only going abroad for a few years.

84
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:29,640
I'm sorry.

85
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,810
I dragged you into this.

86
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:36,080
It's fine.

87
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:38,159
I owe you this.

88
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:43,680
Four years ago,

89
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,610
the suspect I accidentally killed

90
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:47,800
was your brother, right?

91
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:52,000
Yes.

92
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:55,970
Come here, baby.

93
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:09,040
You raped my sister.

94
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,040
You animal!

95
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,570
I'll call the police on you.

96
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,960
Raped your sister?

97
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:16,600
Where is the evidence?

98
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:18,760
Don't think you can cover up everything.

99
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,160
I will find the evidence.

100
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:23,280
So you have no evidence.

101
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,840
But I do.

102
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:31,520
To prove you raped my girlfriend.

103
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:38,159
Nonsense!

104
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:39,400
This is the first time I've seen her.

105
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:40,000
Yes,

106
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:42,679
but you're about to rape her.

107
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:44,360
Go.

108
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,860
Inject him with the aphrodisiac.

109
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:57,840
You're awake.

110
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,760
I just extracted your semen.

111
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:05,560
Now her panties

112
00:09:05,560 --> 00:09:06,620
and inside her body

113
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:10,080
are full of your filthy stuff.

114
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:13,320
So,

115
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:15,740
I'll give you two choices.

116
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:17,360
First,

117
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:20,720
you and your sister keep your mouths shut.

118
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:22,440
Second,

119
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:24,960
I'll send you to prison.

120
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:26,280
Bastard!

121
00:09:26,280 --> 00:09:27,080
I didn't do it!

122
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,280
Is that so?

123
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,720
Then you should ask her.

124
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:34,080
Right.

125
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:35,640
Just now,

126
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,440
you raped me.

127
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:56,920
Later, your brother was furious

128
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:59,400
and took Ding Tian hostage with a knife.

129
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:00,800
I made a misjudgment,

130
00:10:01,040 --> 00:10:02,400
shot your brother dead,

131
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:04,200
and ruined your life.

132
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:13,610
You made a misjudgment,

133
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:15,640
but you were fired because of it.

134
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:19,050
I used your daughter to drag you into this,

135
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,850
which counts as my revenge.

136
00:10:22,560 --> 00:10:23,890
Publicly or privately,

137
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,860
you no longer owe me anything.

138
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:30,300
We handed the flash drive and videotapes to the police.

139
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:33,640
Ding Tian's protective umbrella has been taken down.

140
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,760
He will face trial too.

141
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,600
I have to thank you for all this.

142
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:44,560
Since all of this is over,

143
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:47,970
you should live your life well.

144
00:10:53,520 --> 00:10:54,320
By the way.

145
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:56,960
There is one thing

146
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,820
I have to trouble you with.

147
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:02,000
I want you to help take care of my daughter.

148
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:07,560
I remember she likes tomato and egg noodles,

149
00:11:07,560 --> 00:11:09,220
and likes to add some vinegar.

150
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:11,200
I will make it for her myself.

151
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:30,640
I'll talk.

152
00:11:30,640 --> 00:11:31,840
You listen.

153
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:35,460
Thank you for coming to see me.

154
00:11:35,640 --> 00:11:38,170
Ding Tian's backers have all been taken down.

155
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:40,320
He will soon face trial.

156
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,120
All of this

157
00:11:43,800 --> 00:11:44,800
is over.

158
00:11:50,280 --> 00:11:53,600
I know he hurt you deeply.

159
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:57,690
The physical scars might be hard to erase.

160
00:11:58,400 --> 00:12:00,130
But as for the emotional scars,

161
00:12:00,920 --> 00:12:03,760
I believe you can slowly heal them on your own.

162
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:07,120
Start a fresh new life.

163
00:12:11,040 --> 00:12:11,840
Also,

164
00:12:13,920 --> 00:12:14,960
quit smoking.

165
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:58,880
You look much more energetic than before.

166
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:03,040
Without you guys causing trouble,

167
00:13:03,040 --> 00:13:04,680
I don't have to work my tail off.

168
00:13:04,680 --> 00:13:06,080
With a regular schedule,

169
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:07,850
of course I look energetic.

170
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:12,330
When are you going back?

171
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:13,740
The trial is tomorrow.

172
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:15,240
I will testify in court.

173
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:18,240
After getting this done,

174
00:13:18,800 --> 00:13:20,730
I'll leave the day after tomorrow.

175
00:13:22,520 --> 00:13:23,360
Then,

176
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:25,240
have a safe trip.

177
00:13:27,240 --> 00:13:29,170
Your goodbyes are always so brief.

178
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:36,640
To be honest,

179
00:13:38,280 --> 00:13:39,940
spending these days with you,

180
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:42,000
I really have some feelings for you.

181
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:43,060
What about you?

182
00:13:46,920 --> 00:13:47,720
Is that so?

183
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:51,240
Hearing you say that in my current situation

184
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:53,240
does bring a special kind of warmth.

185
00:13:53,800 --> 00:13:54,600
But,

186
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:57,700
is this your way of comforting me?

187
00:13:58,280 --> 00:14:00,810
It seems you don't want to answer my question.

188
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:08,720
Take care.

189
00:14:09,160 --> 00:14:10,160
I'm leaving.

190
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:16,720
Goodbye.

191
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:10,280
It's all over.

192
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:14,130
Go back and have a good rest.

193
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:37,320
Lighting team.
